OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing during the early evening, then
OL,7,Fclouding over from the west with rain
OL,8,Fspreading east overnight. Feeling
OL,9,Frather cool in the strengthening
OL,10,Fsoutheasterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy and breezy, with rain
OL,13,Fclearing to the east during the
OL,14,Fmorning. Followed by frequent heavy
OL,15,Fshowers in the afternoon before easing
OL,16,Finto the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
